\[LongDash] nonzero sectors,\\n    SimpleSectors[topo1Z] \[LongDash] simple \
sectors (no nonzero subsectors),\\n    BasisSectors[topo1Z] \[LongDash] basis \
sectors (at least one immediate subsector is zero),\\n    ZerojRule[topo1Z] \
\[LongDash] a rule to nullify all zero j[topo1Z\[Ellipsis]],\\n    \
CutDs[topo1Z] \[LongDash] a flag list of cut denominators (1=cut).\"\>"], \
