js[topo1Z,\[Ellipsis]] in UniqueSectors[topo1Z].\\n    jRules[topo1Z,\
\[Ellipsis]] \[LongDash] reduction rules for j[topo1Z,\[Ellipsis]] from \
MappedSectors[topo1Z].\\n    SectorsMappings[topo1Z] gives the list of \
